    {
      "id": "sybil_24_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. You\u2019re going to love how it handles\u2014come take it for a spin!",
