    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_22_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_22",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-maintained and is in wonderful shape for its next owner. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this one won't let you down. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Available is a 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. Powered by the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged engine, this chassis delivers a linear torque curve and sharp throttle response. The power plant remains internally sound with consistent compression across both rotors. The five-speed manual transmission engages precisely, sending power through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Suspension kinematics are preserved with original double-wishbone geometry, offering exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical integrity is prioritized, featuring an upgraded aluminum radiator and silicone vacuum lines to mitigate heat-soak. A rare opportunity for an enthusiast seeking the pure, tactile engagement of a balanced 50/50 weight distribution platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
